com.paypal.selion.reports.runtime

Class MobileReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.reports.runtime.MobileReporter

  • public class MobileReporter
extends Object
    Static log method allow you to create a more meaningful piece of log for a device test. It will log a message and also take a screenshot.
